snippet.title: Taaza Khabar | Season 2 | Official Trailer | Hotstar Specials | Sept 27 | BB Ki Vines Productions
snippet.description:
Don't forget to watch the series "Taaza Khabar" starring Bhuvan Bam, streaming exclusively on Disney+ Hotstar! http://www.hotstar.com/1260127221

Karza aur gunah chukaane padhte hain! Kabhi kabhi marr ke bhi..

Vardaan ya shraap? Kismat ya mehnat? Jeevan ya maut?
Vasya ki kahani ka naya adhyay dekhiye Hotstar Specials Taaza Khabar Season 2 mein, streaming from September 27, only on Disney+ Hotstar.

Disney+ Hotstar's hit fantasy-drama series returns with Hotstar Specials presents Taaza Khabar Season 2, diving deeper into the consequences of Vasya's miraculous gift. Set against the gritty backdrop of Mumbai, this season promises to take viewers on an intense journey as Vasya grapples with the loss of his power and faces life-threatening challenges.

Directed by Himank Gaur and produced by Rohit Raj & Bhuvan Bam under BB Ki Vines Productions, the show continues to be penned by the talented writer duo Hussain Dalal & Abbas Dalal. Bhuvan Bam reprises his role as Vasant Gawde, joined by Shriya Pilgaonkar, Mahesh Manjrekar, Jaaved Jaaferi, Deven Bhojani, Shilpa Shukla, Prathmesh Parab, and Nitya Mathur in pivotal roles.

This season explores the thin line between blessing and curse as Vasya navigates a world where his actions have far-reaching consequences. With higher stakes and deeper emotional complexity, Taaza Khabar Season 2 promises to deliver a gripping tale of redemption, morality, and the human spirit's resilience in the face of adversity.

#TaazaKhabarSeason2 #BBKiVinesProductions #BhuvanBam

ABOUT:
Bhuvan Bam, a multi-talented artist, returns as Vasya in this thrilling new season. To stay updated with Bhuvan's journey and behind-the-scenes content, follow him on:

Jaan Nisar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

7th Sky Entertainmentâ€™s mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznaviâ€™s love?

snippet.title: A Minecraft Movie | Teaser
snippet.description:
Be There and Be Square. #MinecraftMovie - only in theaters 2025

From Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures and starring Jason Momoa and Jack Black, â€œA Minecraft Movie,â€ directed by Jared Hess, is the first-ever big screen, live-action adaptation of Minecraft, the best-selling video game of all time.

The film also stars Emma Myers (â€œWednesdayâ€), Oscar nominee Danielle Brooks (â€œThe Color Purpleâ€), Sebastian Eugene Hansen (â€œJust Mercy, â€œLiseyâ€™s Storyâ€), with Jennifer Coolidge.

Welcome to the world of Minecraft, where creativity doesnâ€™t just help you craft, itâ€™s essential to oneâ€™s survival!  Four misfitsâ€”Garrett â€œThe Garbage Manâ€ Garrison (Momoa), Henry (Hansen), Natalie (Myers) and Dawn (Brooks)â€”find themselves struggling with ordinary problems when they are suddenly pulled through a mysterious portal into the Overworld: a bizarre, cubic wonderland that thrives on imagination.  To get back home, theyâ€™ll have to master this world (and protect it from evil things like Piglins and Zombies, too) while embarking on a magical quest with an unexpected, expert crafter, Steve (Black).  Together, their adventure will challenge all five to be bold and to reconnect with the qualities that make each of them uniquely creativeâ€¦the very skills they need to thrive back in the real world. 

Oscar nominee Hess (â€œNinety-Five Senses,â€ â€œNacho Libreâ€) directed, with Roy Lee, Jon Berg, Mary Parent, Cale Boyter, Jason Momoa, Jill Messick, Torfi Frans Olafsson and Vu Bui producing, and Todd Hallowell, Kayleen Walters, Brian Mendoza, Jonathan Spaihts, Pete Chiappetta, Andrew Lary and Anthony Tittanegro executive producing.

The directorâ€™s creative team behind the camera includes BAFTA-nominated director of photography Enrique Chediak (â€œ127 Hours,â€ â€œTransformers: Rise of the Beastsâ€), Oscar-winning production designer Grant Major (â€œThe Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King,â€ â€œThe Megâ€), editor James Thomas (â€œPokÃ©mon: Detective Pikachuâ€, the â€œBoratâ€ films), Oscar-winning VFX supervisor Dan Lemmon (â€œThe Jungle Book,â€ â€œThe Batmanâ€), and costume designer Amanda Neale (â€œThe Meg,â€ â€œWhat We Do in the Shadowsâ€).  Casting is by Rachel Tenner.  The music supervisors are Gabe Hilfer and Karyn Rachtman, and the music is by Mark Mothersbaugh (â€œThor: Ragnarok,â€ the â€œLEGOÂ®â€ movies).

Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures Present A Vertigo Entertainment/On The Roam/MojÃ¤ng Aktiebolag Production, A Jared Hess Film, â€œA Minecraft Movie.â€  The film will be distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures worldwide and by Legendary East in China, and released only in theaters and IMAX in North America on April 4, 2025, and internationally beginning 2 April 2025.

snippet.description:
Goat (Tamil Movie) - American Theater Experience & Review

Watching "Goat" in the U.S. was electrifying! The theater buzzed with excitement from a diverse audience and the energy was contagious as everyone cheered and reacted together, making it a fun and communal experience.

Review: "Goat" showcases Thalapathy Vijay in a phenomenal dual role, delivering a powerful and versatile performance thatâ€™s the heart of the film. He seamlessly switches between contrasting characters, adding depth and charisma that keeps viewers hooked. Yuvan Shankar Rajaâ€™s background score is a perfect blend, elevating every scene with pulsating beats that amplify the film's intensity and emotional core.

The screenplay is tight and engaging, with unexpected twists that keep the audience on their toes. Venkat Prabhuâ€™s direction is spot-on, expertly balancing action, drama, and humor, making "Goat" a standout experience. While the pacing dips slightly in places, the combination of stellar performances, gripping storytelling, and an unforgettable BGM make "Goat" a must-watch!

Clicks and Cuts - Madhavan
Cuts & Animation - Kamal

Born into a humble family with limited financial resources, Kumar Gaurav Sir faced numerous obstacles throughout his education. Despite these hardships, he worked hard to pursue his dreams. To support himself financially, he started giving tuition classes and gradually moved forward.

After completing his education, Kumar Gaurav Sir joined Utkarsh as a content writer. Through his dedication and hard work, he quickly earned recognition and became one of the top teachers at Utkarsh. His writing skills and unique teaching methods became a source of inspiration for students.

Kumar Gaurav Sir's story teaches us that no matter how difficult life gets, with determination and persistence, any goal can be achieved. His journey encourages us to stay positive and keep moving forward, no matter the obstacles.

Don't miss this video and get inspired by Kumar Gaurav Sir's motivational story to work hard and make your dreams come true.

snippet.title: How To Make Better Decisions? By Sandeep Maheshwari | Hindi
snippet.description:
Sandeep Maheshwari is a name among millions who struggled, failed and surged ahead in search of success, happiness and contentment. Just like any middle class guy, he too had a bunch of unclear dreams and a blurred vision of his goals in life. All he had was an undying learning attitude to hold on to. Rowing through ups and downs, it was time that taught him the true meaning of his life.

To know more, log on to www.sandeepmaheshwari.com

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. snippet.title: Mr. McMahon | Official Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
Mr. McMahon chronicles the rise and fall of Vince McMahon, controversial businessman and co-founder of WWE. From his transformation of the WWE from a small, regional business into a global entertainment powerhouse to the explosive sexual misconduct allegations that led to his eventual resignation, this six-episode series offers a deep dive into McMahonâ€™s life and his enduring franchise. Culled from over 200 hours of interviews with McMahon himself (prior to his resignation), his family members, business associates and some of the most iconic names in wrestling history, as well as the journalists who uncovered McMahonâ€™s allegations â€” filmmaker Chris Smith (Tiger King) and executive producer Bill Simmons (30 for 30) present an unflinching, no-holds-barred look at one of the most enigmatic figures in sports entertainment.

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81179220

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with 278 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Mr. McMahon | Official Trailer | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

WWE experienced record-breaking highs and crushing lows under Vince McMahon's leadership. This docuseries delves into the mogul's controversial reign.

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Watch the full episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSKo8X_EiY0WewaBlNt49g3

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Navina Wadekar / Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

snippet.description:
Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu Chaduvu Biddalu Episode 02 MCM
Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu releases its new episode Chaduvu Biddalu. In this engaging filmymoji video, the middle-class character Madhu and the Naatu Guntala gang navigate their first day in a classroom setting. As the professors commence their lessons, the gang's apprehension about academic pressures mounts, leading them to contemplate abandoning their studies altogether. This relatable narrative captures the challenges faced by students in balancing education and personal concerns, making it a compelling watch for audiences.

Kaffara Episode 39 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 4th September 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.

snippet.title: Visfot | Official Trailer | Streaming 6 September | JioCinema Premium
snippet.description:
Visfot is a gripping crime thriller that explores the dangerous consequences of deceit and poor choices. The film follows the lives of two families, one living in a Mumbai slum and the other in a luxurious high-rise, whoseSS paths intertwine unexpectedly. A series of events leads to a tragic explosion, leaving one man wrongly accused of a crime he didn't commit. As he fights to clear his name, he uncovers a web of corruption and deceit that threatens to destroy everything he holds dear.
